                     CHAP. XV.
The arguments of Papists drawne from reason answered, and retorted.
                     
                        SECT. I.
                        OVr aduersaries are driuen to rake hell for arguments, and to begge proofes from damned hereticks, such as were the Manichees. From whose dissembling at the Lords Supper, our equiuocating Iesuits would make vs beleeue, that their halfe Communion was in vse in the Primitiue Church. The Manichees, 
